  which has maximum absolute error of 0.086 at 2 and maximum relative error of 6.1% at 
  
    
      
        a
      
    
    {\displaystyle a}
  =0.5 and 
  
    
      
        a
      
    
    {\displaystyle a}
  =2.0.
For 
  
    
      
        S
        =
        125348
        =
        1
        
        1110
        
        1001
        
        1010
        
        
          0100
          
            2
          
        
        =
        1.1110
        
        1001
        
        1010
        
        
          0100
          
            2
          
        
        ×
        
          2
          
            16
          
        
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle S=125348=1\;1110\;1001\;1010\;0100_{2}=1.1110\;1001\;1010\;0100_{2}\times 2^{16}\,}
  , the binary approximation gives 
  
    
      
        
          
            S
          
        
        ≈
        (
        0.5
        +
        0.5
        ⋅
        a
        )
