    {\displaystyle Y_{m}=P_{m}^{2}-P_{m+1}^{2}=2P_{m+1}a_{m}+a_{m}^{2}}
  .
Initially, we set 
  
    
      
        
          a
          
            n
          
        
        =
        
          P
          
            n
          
        
        =
        
          2
          
            n
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle a_{n}=P_{n}=2^{n}}
   for the largest 
  
    
      
